Base Blockchain, Coinbase's Ethereum Layer-2 solution, remains one of the strongest performers in 2026. As of late March 2026, its Total Value Locked (TVL) stands at approximately $10.59 billion, leading most Ethereum L2s in DeFi activity and sequencer revenue. 

